snippet.title: We Met in May - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
http://ninasays.so/may
Release date: 9/30/2019 // PC & Mac on Steam & Itch.io

A game collection by Nina Freeman & Jake Jefferies, with music by Ryan Yoshikami.

We met in May and went on a lot of dates. This game is a collection of vignettes about those dates.
